movie_name: The Game Is Up: Disillusioned Trump Voters Tell Their Stories
short_description: A GOP congressman-turned right wing shock jock; a rising star Young Republican; a party-loyal Ohio farmer; a US Army Veteran and 'MAGA'; and three evangelicals all recount their evolution from Trump supporters to adamant adversaries.
